Title: All In
Plot: When a six-year-old boy is brought in with the same symptoms as another patient who died years ago under House's care, House believes the cases are identical and he can predict the course of the boy's illness. Meanwhile, the clinic hosts a poker night to benefit the oncology department.
GuestStars: Laura Allen, Daylon Reese, Purva Bedi, Michelle Harrison, Al Espinosa, Carter Page, MacKenzie Astin
